do, you do what you do.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:07.620
You know, it's just, I, I'm
rambling, but that's what I do.

00:07:07.620 --> 00:07:09.110
I'm sorry.

00:07:09.110 --> 00:07:13.390
But there is a, a line from
Elton John song, Rocket Man,

00:07:13.390 --> 00:07:17.760 position:56%
