00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:23.230
You know, people look at,
you know, he's a rocket man,

00:07:23.230 --> 00:07:25.800
you know, he's an astronaut.

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.350
It's just what he does.

00:07:28.350 --> 00:07:29.830
You know, it's just what I do.

00:07:29.830 --> 00:07:33.820
