Shoot!

00:07:50.810 --> 00:07:52.110
[ Laughter ]

00:07:52.110 --> 00:07:53.410
In the summer I was a pool boy.

00:07:53.410 --> 00:07:55.040
[ Laughter ]

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:56.340
I was good at that.

