00:09:32.610 --> 00:09:33.910
That's, yeah --

00:09:33.910 --> 00:09:35.210
[ Applause ]

00:09:35.210 --> 00:09:37.380
That became the greatest
day of my life, you know.

00:09:37.380 --> 00:09:40.040
