00:10:37.090 --> 00:10:39.510
I mean he means something
to you, right!

00:10:39.510 --> 00:10:42.090
[ Laughter ]

00:10:42.090 --> 00:10:44.630
I got, don't care to twist it.

00:10:44.630 --> 00:10:45.930
Yeah, but so, he, you know,

00:10:45.930 --> 00:10:47.800
he understood that,
that, that you know.

00:10:47.800 --> 00:10:49.610
He understands his
place in our history.

00:10:49.610 --> 00:10:51.890
There was no doubt in
that moment for me.

00:10:51.890 --> 00:10:56.050
And, but, but what an honor.

00:10:56.050 --> 00:11:01.040
Wow! Another one would
be Chuck Brown, you know.

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:04.880
Yeah. Chuck's, Chuck, I
