Ben's Chili Bowl, and,

00:11:16.570 --> 00:11:18.150
which is pretty cool to me.

00:11:18.150 --> 00:11:20.170
But Chuck was just
such a cool brother.

00:11:20.170 --> 00:11:24.550
Listened to my show every
morning, four hours every morning,

00:11:24.550 --> 00:11:26.790
every morning, was
just the coolest guy.

00:11:26.790 --> 00:11:31.700
I still have not been able to
bring myself to watch his Unsung.

00:11:31.700 --> 00:11:34.490
It's taped, but I haven't, they
asked me to be a part of it

00:11:34.490 --> 00:11:35.790
