00:11:35.790 --> 00:11:37.090
I just, I don't know.

00:11:37.090 --> 00:11:39.330
It was kind of emotional for me.

00:11:39.330 --> 00:11:41.880
And so, but, but I will watch it.

00:11:41.880 --> 00:11:44.770
But Chuck was just such a,
just such a cool brother,

00:11:44.770 --> 00:11:50.990
and so about D.C. You know, and
I, and I guess that takes me

00:11:50.990 --> 00:11:54.100
