[ Applause ]

00:11:58.310 --> 00:11:59.610
You know, yeah.

00:11:59.610 --> 00:12:01.690
And, and people around the country
sometimes don't understand it.

00:12:01.690 --> 00:12:03.820
They go you know how you
support that guy, you know.

00:12:03.820 --> 00:12:06.060
It's like, shoot, man, please.

00:12:06.060 --> 00:12:07.830
It's a D.C. thing.

00:12:07.830 --> 00:12:14.440 position:56%
