down, you know.

00:12:37.250 --> 00:12:40.360
And so that night I called
my dad and I was crying.

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:42.230
I was just, you know,
telling him what happened.

00:12:42.230 --> 00:12:44.170
They had this thing
on video tape, dad.

00:12:44.170 --> 00:12:46.370
Well, blah, blah, blah,
went on and on.

00:12:46.370 --> 00:12:51.510
Finally my dad said, Mmmm.

00:12:51.510 --> 00:12:58.140
[ Laughter ]

00:12:58.140 --> 00:12:59.940
And that was it.

00:12:59.940 --> 00:13:04.040
[ Laughter ]

00:13:04.040 --> 00:13:08.180
So I'm, I'm in the process of
writing a book now, and that's part

00:13:08.180 --> 00:13:11.870
of what I want to write about, and
it's just called Mmm, that part,

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:17.450
because, because when you live that
long and seen that much, you know,

